metaData.Key Information: These Sea Scallops are also known as Diver Scallops. Traditionally harvested by divers who jump into the water and collect them by hand. But now most scallops are harvested by boats dragging chain nets across the ocean floor. The US scallops are size based on per pound, eg 10-20 size means there are 10-20 pc per lb. Scallops are known best for grilling but there are unlimited ways to prepare this.
